  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age 18 or older

          -  Probable ischemic stroke within prior 14 days

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Any medical condition precluding the avoidance of supine posture or dictating the need
             for a particular position.

          -  Current use of CPAP (or other PAP), mechanical ventilation, or supplemental oxygen.
      </textblock>
